manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "zero2prod"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/health_check.rs"
name = "health_check"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "zero2prod"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Alexander Zafirov <alexander@zafirov.me>"]
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
actix-http = "3.0.0-beta.15"
actix-web = "4.0.0-beta.14"
chrono = "0.4.15"
config = "0.11.0"
tracing-actix-web = "=0.5.0-beta.9"
tracing-bunyan-formatter = "0.3"
tracing-log = "0.1"

[dependencies.secrecy]
version = "0.8"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.5.7"
features = ["runtime-actix-rustls", "macros", "postgres", "uuid", "chrono", "migrate", "offline"]
optional = false
default-features = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
features = ["log"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["registry", "env-filter"]
optional = false

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "0.8.1"
features = ["v4"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies]
actix-rt = "2.5.0"
once_cell = "1"
reqwest = "0.11"
tokio = "1.14.0"

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []
